feat: Add client-state, thread-state, and recording-level metrics

{body}

Added new metrics for Kafka Streams: client-state, thread-state, and recording-level as part of KAFKA-17561. The client-state metric tracks the current state of the Kafka Streams client, the thread-state metric provides the state of each StreamThread, and the recording-level metric reflects the current metrics recording level.

fix: handle missing optional fields to prevent NullPointerException [KAFKA-9192]

Prevent NullPointerException when optional fields are missing in JSON payload. Adds null check for jsonValue before accessing its null status to handle optional fields correctly.

